Hmmm -- that page was just for GPT wire with insulation rated at 85 degC
(185 degF). GXL or SXL rated at 125 degC (257 degF) might be better for
anything that goes in the engine compartment.

http://www.anaheimwire.com/gxl1.htm

http://www.anaheimwire.com/SXLCROSSLINK.htm

